products.title: Bananarama Aluminium Venetian
products.description: The bright and zesty yellow aluminium blind is perfect for lifting and adding some colour to a room. Use this in your kitchen to brighten up every morning. Coming with a matching yellow headrail, this blind is a burst of colour in any window. Keep your blinds looking their best with their easy to wipe clean aluminium slats, just use a damp cloth to wipe away any dirt or stains. Raise and lower your blind to the perfect height, and then angle the venetian slats to control the light entering your home.
